column1: # Supplemental File S14 - Sub-Genomic RNA Counts From Clinical SARS-CoV-2 Samples Using Illumina Bait Capture
# Counts of canonical sub-genomic RNA from clinical SARS-CoV-2 samples selected by bait capture and sequenced using Illumina technology
# amplicons: The amplicon(s) that gave rise to the sub-genomic RNA
# sgRNA_count: The number of noncanonical sub-genomic reads at this ORF
# coverage: Average coverage in a wiondow around ORF start site
# sgRPTL: Noncanonical sub-genomic reads per thousand around ORF start site (coverage)
# sgRPHT: Noncanonical sub-genomic reads per hundred thousand mapped reads
